{"tid":971414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"O記檢槍械武器　3人被捕","createTime":"2019-01-06T15:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T16:13:34.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3a3985e02847f0c1ef3b7b6541952a31a1090c31","tid":971414,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:13:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190106/s00001/62231b29c153fa5a8b6ffb6a937e83f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190106%2Fs00001%2F62231b29c153fa5a8b6ffb6a937e83f0.jpg&h=4aaa54c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方有組織罪案及三合會調查科（O記）日前採取行動，檢獲一批槍械及武器，共拘2男1女。<br />\n<br />\n行動中，一名30歲本地男子涉嫌「無牌管有槍械及彈藥」被捕，他已被落案起訴，案件明日（7日）在西九龍裁判法院提堂。另外兩名分別52歲及62歲的本地男女，涉嫌「藏有攻擊性武器」被捕，兩人已獲准保釋候查，須於1月中旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\nO記根據線報及深入調查後，前日（4日）突擊搜查全港6處處所，檢獲一批槍械及武器，包括手槍、長槍、電槍、槍械組件、逾百發子彈殼、軍刀及手鐐。"},{"pid":"19b4754b3c37ec9166e5c34a1f1d9ed3bb54c4bc","tid":971414,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:17:35.000Z","msg":"係唔係AR15黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"428bc8b8ee7b919fdf119bd0702247c32ab8dd8c","tid":971414,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:19:07.000Z","msg":"氣槍黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a96632c2f0cd6cddfa7f9cb17ed21bd8312d4bc","tid":971414,"uid":16061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:21:57.000Z","msg":"逾百發子彈<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">殼</span></span>"},{"pid":"19e0c7ab77f3a1b5c91d3b1aede6943f4e8281cd","tid":971414,"uid":63515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:35:16.000Z","msg":"咁似氣槍既？ 係咪過兩焦耳就搵條罪告呀？"},{"pid":"868a7a6189dcfac3d97cf4e60e38f659f6745f3f","tid":971414,"uid":28669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a96632c2f0cd6cddfa7f9cb